<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
  <div class="carousel-indicators">
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
  </div>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="review carousel-item active">
      <div class="review-title">
        <p><strong>Skirt Repair</strong></p>
        <div class="d-flex stars">
          <% 5.times do %>
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-img">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dq1xs22hk/image/upload/v1645738596/profile/isabelle.jpg"/>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">
        <p>Rey is the best! She repaired the zipper on my favorite skirt. She made my skirt like new, I didn't have to spend money to buy a new skirt. I'll definitely do business with her again. Thanks Rey!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="date">
        <p><em>Isabelle, 2022-01-28</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review carousel-item">
      <div class="review-title">
        <p><strong>Trousers Repair</strong></p>
        <div class="d-flex stars">
          <% 5.times do %>
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-img">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dq1xs22hk/image/upload/v1645738592/profile/cameron.jpg"/>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">
        <p>She fixed the waist of my trousers and was ready to pick up 2 days later, Rey is efficient and oriented on the details.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="date">
        <p><em>Cameron, 2022-03-07</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review carousel-item">
      <div class="review-title">
        <p><strong>Wedding Dress Repair</strong></p>
        <div class="d-flex stars">
          <% 5.times do %>
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-img">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dq1xs22hk/image/upload/v1645738587/profile/laura.jpg"/>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">
        <p>Rey repaired all the buttons on my wedding dress, I couldn't find anyone near me, thank you Rey!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="date">
        <p><em>Kathy, 2022-02-25</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
